<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Juett Tech Rescue</title>

<style>
body {
  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  background: #f8f5ef;
}

.container {
  width: 90%;
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: auto;
}

h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
.green { color: #2f7d32; }

.btn {
  background: #2f7d32;
  color: white;
  padding: 12px 18px;
  border-radius: 25px;
  text-decoration: none;
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 10px;
}

.card {
  background: white;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 15px;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

form {
  display: grid;
  gap: 12px;
}

input, textarea, select {
  padding: 10px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<h1>Declutter your <span class="green">electronic waste</span>, responsibly.</h1>

<p>$25 flat fee pickup — we come to you.</p>

<a href="#form" class="btn">Schedule Pickup</a>

<div class="card">
<h2>What We Take</h2>
<ul>
<li>Phones & iPhones</li>
<li>Laptops & computers</li>
<li>TVs</li>
<li>Speakers & audio</li>
<li>Cords & chargers</li>
<li>Anything that plugs in or uses a battery</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div id="form" class="card">
<h2>Schedule Pickup</h2>

<form action="https://formspree.io/f/myknpeyk" method="POST">

<input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New Pickup Request">

<input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
<input type="tel" name="phone" placeholder="Phone Number" required>
<input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email (optional)">

<input type="text" name="address" placeholder="Pickup Address" required>

<textarea name="electronics" placeholder="What electronics do you have?" required></textarea>

<select name="day" required>
<option value="">Select Day</option>
<option>Friday</option>
<option>Saturday</option>
<option>Sunday</option>
</select>

<select name="time" required>
<option value="">Select Time</option>
<option>9–11 AM</option>
<option>11–1 PM</option>
<option>1–3 PM</option>
<option>3–5 PM</option>
</select>

<textarea name="notes" placeholder="Extra instructions (optional)"></textarea>

<button type="submit" class="btn">Request Pickup</button>

</form>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>